ng along his left side, Nospiratus picked up his pen and dutifully recorded the vision he had seen.  As for the rest, this recent dialogue with his Master would not be shared with anyone...except the one that casued him to act with such foolish abandon.  He had learned what he had to know - he still had the power of foresight and the visions were still channeled through Hate.  But he had learned other things as well.  Feeling the couldron burning white hot in his own black heart, Nospiratus smiled as he recorded his visions and his prophecy.  No more riddles it seemed - the meaning was clear.  <br><br>At the bottom of the page, Nospiratus wrote, &quot;The city of Qeynos will fall to darkness, fire and sword, but the people of that land will bow to a word form the clarion voice of Nimhiriel Innoroki.  Upon that day, dark chains will be shattered.&quot;<br><br>Nospiratus smiled, wincing form the pain that lingered upon his body from the power unleashed upon him by the laughter of Hate.  Nospiratus smiled, feeling the gift within his heart as it fed the cauldron of his purifying Hate.  Their time was nearly at hand.<br><br>Nospiratus K'Thalion<br>Mad Prophet of Hate <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/fvhbrellfrm3.showNextMessage?topicID=241.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/fvhbrellfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=241.topic&index=1><img src=http://www.violentharvest.com/reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/fvhbrellfrm3.emailToFriend?topicID=241.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/fvhbrellfrm3.threadControl?topicID=241.topic><img src=http:/